How do I run other Vitest tests alongside my Storybook tests Some projects have other tests run via Vitest, e g unit tests, in addition to those defined in Storybook You can run these tests independently by specifying the project filter in a separate script For example, for a Vitest project called ‚Äúunit‚Äù:
